snippet.title: A Pretty Odd Bunny - Xbox One Gameplay
snippet.description:
AJ Ordaz and 2Awesome Partners brought this 2D stealth platformer to Xbox One in 2021. Developed using Construct 3, you play as a red eyed bunny who is allergic to carrots. What does he eat instead? Pigs!

Guess that bnuuy is more into bacon than anything.

A Pretty Odd Bunny (C) AJ Ordaz
Xbox store page: https://www.xbox.com/en-ie/games/store/a-pretty-odd-bunny/9nn60ktqc3pn

Also available on Steam, PS4 and Switch.
